adcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=18f0af13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"49579f6798b098d482d086539d7c67c1a2c32a90","tid":1232621,"uid":193138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}